  "3277440": {
    "name": "许愿岛 Hope Isle Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3277440,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你正在浏览的是《许愿岛》的试玩版商店页面，试玩版游戏包括如下限制内容：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的小岛上<strong>最多</strong>只会出现<strong>6个“</strong>祈灵”小动物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的小岛只能解锁部分建筑</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于这款游戏的正式版</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/4e9daa7b898fed9f5b29094de528840a.poster.avif?t=1753166590\" width=615 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/4e9daa7b898fed9f5b29094de528840a.webm?t=1753166590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在某一天，忧伤之海中长出了一颗高耸入云的希望之树，在这棵树底部逐渐形成了一座小岛，也就是我们的许愿岛。您可以在游戏中写下心愿，岛上的祈灵们会为了愿望成真而虔诚祈祷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“有的愿望只适合藏在心里”，如果您不希望让你写下的愿望总是被别人看到，也可以把愿望切换为<strong>加密符文</strong>。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/e8217d032c3ce90a9322db2aeba0da9e.webp?t=1753166590\" width=358 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现这座岛的人就是许愿岛的主人，也就是您。您可以召唤更多的祈灵，亦可以建设和扩张这座岛，把它建造成为祈灵们的乐园。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于这座岛存在于另外一个位面，岛主只能通过一束光来和岛上的诸多事物进行交互，祈灵们也要通过这束光来感受岛主的关注和呵护。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/e27858367f4fc5f33673b36fab08a2df.poster.avif?t=1753166590\" width=617 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/e27858367f4fc5f33673b36fab08a2df.webm?t=1753166590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/8c300c74eac82e161b49b041488f60bd.webp?t=1753166590\" width=519 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >岛屿附近的海域里物产丰富，岛上肥沃的土壤也适宜种植多种作物，通过钓鱼、耕种和商店获取这些物资。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着流程推进，您还将解锁烹饪和制作功能，利用物资制作祈灵们喜欢的食物和玩具，丰富他们的生活。他们的快乐和满足将会是岛主的宝贵财富，也会更加卖力为您的愿望祈祷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/baa020f8ac1ad6463f8929d887157bc2.poster.avif?t=1753166590\" width=591 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/baa020f8ac1ad6463f8929d887157bc2.webm?t=1753166590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/5a1ea744e87e290f01845fc40ad5d7ad.webp?t=1753166590\" width=396 height=41 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >祈祷是祈灵们与生俱来的工作，在工作之余祈灵们也会享受他们的个人时光，在岛主设计的小世界里任意休憩或玩耍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于性格各异，在岛上偶然相遇的他们可以成为挚友亦可能关系紧张。您需要在闲暇之余照看岛民的心情，适当的投下光柱，引导这些小生灵解决他们的烦恼，或者和它们分享当下的快乐与满足！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/f8aacaf81afed39f7cc95ce80f61177b.poster.avif?t=1753166590\" width=612 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/f8aacaf81afed39f7cc95ce80f61177b.webm?t=1753166590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/cdbe5044865fea25685457ef48ae6647.webp?t=1753166590\" width=337 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >工作学习的时候可以打开“专注时钟”功能把许愿岛放在屏幕一角，让它成为你管理时间的好伙伴。虽然实现美好心愿多半是要靠努力奋斗，但许愿岛会一直默默为你祝福。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/434cfadcfe79e83cfdcd30e1ddea7f35.avif?t=1753166590\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras_big/434cfadcfe79e83cfdcd30e1ddea7f35.avif?t=1753166590 width=1600 height=752 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了在岛上和祈灵们相会，您也可以把它们<i>召唤到电脑桌面</i>上，让它们在游戏之外陪你度过忙碌的时光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/fcadb23c28822b97473463b39bcd672b.poster.avif?t=1753166590\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/fcadb23c28822b97473463b39bcd672b.webm?t=1753166590\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277440/extras/fcadb23c28822b97473463b39bcd672b.mp4?t=1753166590\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
